<div class="cta-contact">
  <h2>Book a Dog-Friendly Room in Vernal</h2>
  <p>Pet rooms are limited — call ahead to confirm availability and lock in your dates.</p>
  <div class="contact-options">
    <a href="tel:4357896625" class="contact-opt"><span class="icon">📞</span><span class="lbl">Call Us</span><span class="val">(435) 789-6625</span></a>
    <a href="sms:4357896625" class="contact-opt"><span class="icon">💬</span><span class="lbl">Text or WhatsApp</span><span class="val">(435) 789-6625</span></a>
    <a href="https://bestwesternvernalinn.com" class="contact-opt book"><span class="icon">🌐</span><span class="lbl">Book Online</span><span class="val">bestwesternvernalinn.com</span></a>
